                <p><img class="img-responsive" src="https://i.imgur.com/fh3ybtK.png"></p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="modal-body">
                <h5><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-4">-</i> Fourth Step:</strong> Copy the link shown on bottom right by pressing on the <i class="fa-solid fa-copy"></i></a>
