                <p><img class="img-responsive" src="https://i.imgur.com/L24jqg2.png"></p>
              </div>

              <div class="modal-body">
                <h5><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-6">-</i> Last Step:</strong> By clicking "Send to Patient", The meeting will be sent to the patient and you will be redirected back to home page</i></a>
                <p><img class="img-responsive" src="https://i.imgur.com/1Dcle0J.png"></p>
              </div>

              <!-- Modal footer -->
              <div class="modal-footer">
